00:29:22.000Z","msg":"共產黨只有衰人同更衰既人<br />\n<br />\n___________________________________<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">大陸有新SARS? 唔好比我估中，快睇「軍事」「香港」「漫畫多圖」《最終解決方案》已更新到第七章，入去留名推下啦。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1615112\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1615112</a></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/ANEXGUt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FANEXGUt.png&h=7a431701&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T02:39:37.000Z","msg":"你幅圖啲字好細隻，有冇清晰版？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T03:12:34.000Z","msg":"冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />成套都係咁，建議用手機睇"},{"pid":"3c4a72d45b7ddaa983d0866089f2464f9fd41098","tid":1809102,"uid":41260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T03:28:56.000Z","msg":"老鼠成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nBtw「當年」嘅民主派真係有做嘢<br />\n依家嘅就<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73cb4cb00bd4088bcd6b80a938540fecaa944c3c","tid":1809102,"uid":235501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T03:29:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e05293323d2d900c5d24438e8654f28dd1b14e62","tid":1809102,"uid":39383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T03:48:16.000Z","msg":"畜牲!"},{"pid":"30e1fb9c0282874ef38952e058317f3558d57279","tid":1809102,"uid":161684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T03:49:17.000Z","msg":"諗起之前條紀錄片李柱銘果段<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7ece1e6d48dbe4aba9ec436142801b06c489d5e","tid":1809102,"uid":8543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3aca330f783a14bfa3857bbb4f88fd8f82689ed8","tid":1809102,"uid":63936,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"efb9efc8cfab14613c6c03047fc052944c614ab2","tid":1809102,"uid":251945,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T01:16:03.000Z","msg":"所以當年民主派做左咩？